      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>Catering kitchen, Pasadena. Wolf Commercial 6-burner modular cooktop, 6 years old.</h3>
        <p>3 burners sluggish, 3 normal. Diagnosed: burner head clog from grease and carbon buildup on the affected burners (high prep volume, no scheduled cleaning). Cleaned all 6 burner heads (preventive on the 3 still-clean ones), replaced 1 igniter that was weakening. Total: $120 plus $185 parts plus $335 cleaning labor = $640.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>Mexican restaurant, East LA. Imperial 4-burner standalone, 8 years old.</h3>
        <p>Pilot system unreliable plus 2 burners with weak ignition. Diagnosed: pilot system end-of-life (older standing-pilot unit) plus 2 burner igniters at year 8 wear. Serviced pilot system, replaced 2 igniters. Total: $120 plus $260 parts plus 1.5 hours = $560.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

